replies.body:
Malphite needs a rework, at least for satisfaction purposes. To me he's just an ult-bot, and {{champion:12}} {{champion:497}} and even {{champion:516}} arguably do as good if not better job than Malphite when it comes to teamfight initiation and utility with their knock-ups on much shorter cooldowns and more useful basic abilities. He needs a Sejuani-like update where there is less power in ult so his basic abilities feel good to use.

Also, how come Malphite doesn't have any % current/max HP abilities? Most if not all tanks do % dmg or shred resistances. The only tank I can think of that doesn't have that is Nautilus and that's because he has a CC-heavy kit and a shield he can activate at will that scales up with level. Do you think adding % dmg to his abilities or a bonus HP ratio besides his passive would help him at all?

Don't forget about {{champion:106}}
